These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, japanese, australian, spanish, british, pakistani
1. the colombian is in the middle##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the australian##1
4. the indonesian is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the pakistani is on the far left##1
6. the british is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | australian | spanish | colombian | japanese | indonesian | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, software-developer, lawyer, designer, dancer, dressmaker, writer
1. the writer is on the far right##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the lawyer##1
5. the designer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
6. the writer is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | electrician | dancer | lawyer | dressmaker | designer | software-developer | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, cooking, filmmaking, baking, collecting, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | baking | camping | collecting | cooking | magic-tricks | chess | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
