.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, bird, cat, chinchilla, rat, pony
1. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | pony | bird | cat | rat | ferret | fish | chinchilla |

