1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | documentary | zombie | epic | scientific | family | fantasy |

